                            >NSC</gloss> Institutional Files (<gloss target="#t_H1"
                        >H</gloss>–Files), Box <gloss target="#t_H1">H</gloss>–107, Verification
                        Panel Minutes Originals 1969–3/8/72. Top Secret; Sensitive. The meeting took
